<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.10">
<l>cakka rattaṇ ṇalēyeṉṟu tāḻntu kaṇṇīr tatumpa</l>
<l>pakka nōkki niṉṟa lantēṉ pāviyēṉ kāṇkiṉṟilēṉ</l>
<l>mikka ñāṉa mūrtti yāya vēta viḷakkiṉaiyeṉ</l>
<l>takka ñāṉak kaṇka ḷālē kaṇṭu taḻuvuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying “o majesty with the discus”, lowering myself while tears overflow,</l>
<l>looking to the side, I constantly suffered, I sinner don’t see.</l>
<l>Will I see [and] embrace with the eyes of knowledge that is suited to me</l>
<l>the lamp of the Vedas that is the form of abundant knowledge?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
